## 基本使用

```tsx
/**
 * background: '#f8f8f8'
 */
import React from 'react';
import { CrudModelRender } from 'lyr-low-code';

export default () => {
  return (
    <CrudModelRender
      type="table"
      schema=""
      services=""
    />
  );
};
```

## 注入依赖

```tsx
/**
 * background: '#f8f8f8'
 */
import React from 'react';
import { CrudModelRender } from 'lyr-low-code';

export default () => {
  return (
    <CrudModelRender
      type="table"
      schema=""
      require={{
        hello: () => {
          console.log('hello');
        },
      }}
    />
  );
};
```
